---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Car Rental Downtown Dubai 2026 — From AED 35/day"
  description="Compare car rentals near Downtown Dubai, Burj Khalifa, and Dubai Mall. Delivery included. Economy from AED 35/day."
>
<div class="bg-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 mb-2">📍 Downtown Dubai</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Car Rental Downtown Dubai — From AED 35/day</h1>
  <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare car rental companies near Burj Khalifa, Dubai Mall, and the Dubai Opera district.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=downtown-dubai" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Get Downtown Car Rental Quotes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-4 mb-10">
    <iframe src="https://www.discovercars.com/engine/rent-a-car/iframe?a_aid=YOUR_AFFILIATE_ID&location=Downtown+Dubai&lang=en&curr=AED" width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="Downtown Dubai Car Rental — Compare Prices"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Car Rental in Downtown Dubai</h2>
    <p>Downtown Dubai is the city's commercial and tourist heart, anchored by Burj Khalifa and the Dubai Mall. Car rental companies deliver directly to Downtown hotels and residences, with economy options from AED 35/day.</p>
    <p>Downtown is centrally located with excellent road access to Business Bay, DIFC, and Sheikh Zayed Road. A rental car from Downtown puts you within 15 minutes of Dubai Marina, 20 minutes of the airport, and 25 minutes of Palm Jumeirah.</p>
    <p>Valet parking is widely available at Downtown hotels and malls. Street parking is metered via the RTA mParking app at AED 4/hour.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/car-rentals" class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all car rental areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
